utational anaphora resolution and its application in text retrieval, rules for resolving non-finite clause anaphors are established. Therefore, this book shows that a truly interdisciplinary approach can achieve results which would not have been possible otherwise. Open Access: In July 2019, this volume was retroactively turned into an Open Access publication thanks to the support of the Fachinformationsdienst Linguistik.https://www.linguistik.de/  aIssued also in print.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aThis eBook is made available Open Access under a CC BY-NC 4.0 license: uhttps://creativecommons.org/licenses/by-nc/4.0 uhttps://www.degruyter.com/dg/page/open-access-policy  aIn English.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 01. Dez 2022) 0aAnaphora (Linguistics). 0aComputational linguistics. 0aDiscourse analysisxTechnological innnovations. 0aEnglish languagexAnaphora. 0aEnglish languagexTechological innovations. 4aAnapher (Syntax). 4aHypertext. 4aText-Retrieval. 7aLANGUAGE ARTS & DISCIPLINES / Linguistics / Syntax.2bisacsh  aAnaphora.  aHypertexts.  aText Retrieval.08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertDG Plus DeG Package 2015 Part 1z978311076251808iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertDG Plus eBook-Package 2015z978311070098508iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE COMPLETE 2015z9783110439687oZDB-23-DGG08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE Linguistics 2015z9783110438710oZDB-23-DSP0 cEPUBz97831104168170 cprintz978311041674940uhttps://doi.org/10.1515/9783110416756zOpen Access7040uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9783110416756zOpen Access70423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/document/cover/isbn/9783110416756/original  a978-3-11-070098-5 DG Plus eBook-Package 2015b2015  a978-3-11-076251-8 DG Plus DeG Package 2015 Part 1b2015  aGBV-deGruyter-alles  aZDB-23-DGG